grade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003eKaterina Kantalis\u003c/a\u003e, garden designer who specialises in Mediterranean outdoor spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e;Unlike other Mediterranean gardens from Italy, France, or Spain, which can often be more formal, with bold colours and lots of detail, in my view, Greek gardens tend to be much more modest and connected to nature.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-how-to-achive-the-look\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHow to achive the look\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo create a Greek garden at home you’ll obviously want to opt for the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/best-plants-for-a-mediterranean-garden\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/best-plants-for-a-mediterranean-garden\"\u003ebest Mediterranean plants\u003c/a\u003e such as lavender, rosemary, thyme and jasmine.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNot only do these plants look amazing, but they\u0026#39;re also some of the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/best-scented-shrubs\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/best-scented-shrubs\"\u003ebest-smelling shrubs\u003c/a\u003e you can buy to fill your garden with a gorgeous scent.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BaSsM337Wng5oP2oLFuGKE-415-80.png