our plant pots for your \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/landscaping/container-garden-ideas\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/landscaping/container-garden-ideas\"\u003econtainer garden\u003c/a\u003e and opting for lightly-coloured stone when choosing your patio slabs, pathways or gravel.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Add a few architectural elements, like a small pergola or a classic urn, and keep things uncluttered to let the space breathe,\u0026#39; advises Luke. \u0026#39;Even just \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/decor\" data-auto-tag-linker=\"true\" data-before-rewrite-redirect=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/tag/paint\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/decor\"\u003epainting\u003c/a\u003e a wall white or adding some blue accents can evoke that Greek island feel. With a few thoughtful changes, you can bring a bit of the Mediterranean to your own backyard.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT.jpg\" alt=\"Lavender growing outside house in borders and pot\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zr72vAHnucC7DfnsEBqVkT.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003eNot only does it smell delicious, but lavender is an important of any Greek garden.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC/Polly Eltes Photography)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘As for whether this is a lasting trend, I believe it is. The principles behind Greek gardens—simplicity, sustainability, and a connection to nature—have enduring appeal.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;As we face more extreme weather and water shortages, gardens that require less water and upkeep are only going to become more attractive.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"section-get-the-look\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGet the look\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"72dfb039-0115-4209-98f6-7657af82214d\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=7833\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-8757544076672910740\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crocus.co.uk%2Fproduct%2F_%2Fterracotta-erigeron-pot-small%2Fclassid.2000046529%2Fsku.PR30015